OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779444433
OL,3,CEx-Green candidate for Makerfield
OL,4,Capologises for sharing 'false flag'
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FThe Green Party said its former
OL,8,Fcandidate in the Makerfield by-
OL,9,Felection had apologised after a report
OL,10,Fthat he had shared a post calling an
OL,11,Fattack on Jewish ambulances in north
OL,12,FLondon a "false flag".
OL,14,FChris Kennedy was announced to be
OL,15,Frunning in the seat for the Greens on
OL,16,Fthe morning of Thursday, 21 May, but
OL,17,Fthe party confirmed he had dropped out
OL,18,Fsome nine hours later, citing
OL,19,F"personal and family reasons".
OL,26,@tD@JOUtD@UO]{D@AOU{D@]O]
