PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779444433
OL,3,CEx-Green candidate for Makerfield
OL,4,Capologises for sharing 'false flag'
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FThe Times later reported it had
OL,8,Fapproached Mr Kennedy about a series
OL,9,Fof social media posts he had shared.
OL,11,FA Green Party spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"These posts don't reflect the views
OL,13,Fof The Green Party.
OL,15,F"We have spoken to Chris about these
OL,16,Fposts, and he has now deleted them. He
OL,17,Fapologises for the offence caused."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@AOUyD@cO]
