PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779444433
OL,3,CEx-Green candidate for Makerfield
OL,4,Capologises for sharing 'false flag'
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FAccording to the newspaper, an
OL,8,FInstagram video shared by Mr Kennedy
OL,9,Fdescribed the arrests of two men over
OL,10,Fthe incident as "total bull**** to
OL,11,Fkeep the false flag flying".
OL,13,FA "false flag" operation is generally
OL,14,Fdescribed as staging an attack and
OL,15,Ffalsely blaming a group in an effort
OL,16,Fto shift public opinion.
OL,18,FEssa Suleiman, 45, has been charged
OL,19,Fwith the attempted murders of three
OL,20,Fpeople during the two knife attacks in
OL,21,FLondon.
OL,26,@rD@QOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
