PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779444433
OL,3,CEx-Green candidate for Makerfield
OL,4,Capologises for sharing 'false flag'
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FThe Times also says he also shared a
OL,8,Fpost by a user named Hugh Anthony, a
OL,9,Fself-described "proud ethno-
OL,10,Fnationalist", which said the response
OL,11,Fto the Golders Green arson attack in
OL,12,FMarch made "no sense".
OL,14,FThe Green Party said its earlier
OL,15,Fstatement still stood on the
OL,16,Fwithdrawal of Mr Kennedy, a nurse and
OL,17,Fchildren's safeguarding specialist.
OL,19,FThe party said previously: "We wish
OL,20,FChris the best and understand that
OL,21,Ffamily has to come first.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@LO]tD@LOUtD@UO]{D@\OU
