OL,3,CEx-Green candidate for Makerfield
OL,4,Capologises for sharing 'false flag'
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,F"As a party, we are re-opening
OL,8,Fnominations now because we believe
OL,9,Fpeople in Makerfield deserve a real
OL,10,Fchoice at this by-election, and the
OL,11,FGreen Party will be standing to offer
OL,12,Fexactly that.
OL,14,F"Across the country, more and more
OL,15,Fvoters are turning away from the old
OL,16,Fparties and looking for politicians
OL,17,Fwho will genuinely stand up for their
OL,18,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
