PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779444433
OL,3,CEx-Green candidate for Makerfield
OL,4,Capologises for sharing 'false flag'
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,F"We will also be redoubling our
OL,8,Fefforts on campaigning to expose the
OL,9,Frisk of Reform, a party who seeks to
OL,10,Fdivide our communities.
OL,12,F"This election has to be about how to
OL,13,Fmake the super-rich pay their fair
OL,14,Fshare, how we tackle the cost-of-
OL,15,Fliving crisis with lower bills and
OL,16,Faffordable housing, and how we protect
OL,17,Four public services and our green
OL,18,Fspaces.
OL,20,F"It has to be about offering
OL,21,FMakerfield hope over hate."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU|D@AOU}D@[O]
